{"article_id":"TPWbqhNUJfMZ7Qo5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senator Susan Collins speaks to reporters","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"after announcing her support for the confirmation of Brett Kavanaugh to the Supreme Court ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"October 5 , 2018 .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"( Yuri Gripas/Reuters )","depth":2},{"id":4,"text":"We are not prone to praising Susan Collins .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"But we are delighted to make an exception for her impressive speech on the Senate floor this afternoon","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"explaining why she ' ll vote \" yes \" on Brett Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"A process","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that has often been disgusting","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"- exposing the bottomless bad faith of Senate Democrats and the hysterical partisanship of much of the mainstream media -","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"reached the beginning of the end with a careful , thoughtful , and persuasive presentation by Senator Collins .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"She rightly excoriated the last few weeks as akin to \" a gutter-level political campaign. \"","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"She was appropriately angry over the charges","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"surfaced by guttersnipe attorney Michael Avenatti","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"that Judge Kavanaugh was allegedly part of a gang-rape ring as a teenager","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"- a charge","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"that ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"lest we forget ,","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"was taken seriously by the press and Democrats .","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"She blasted whoever on the Democratic side leaked to the press Dr. Ford ' s letter to the committee .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"On Ford ' s allegation , she got to the crux of the matter :","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"The witnesses","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"that Ford named","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"have no memory of such a party ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"and no one has come forward","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"who does .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"( We will note","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"that Kavanaugh categorically denied being at such a party","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"before he knew what Ford ' s friend , Leland Keyser , would say","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"- taking a great risk","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"unless he was sincere and truthful in his denial . )","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"There are key gaps in Ford ' s account ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"including not knowing","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"how she got home from the party in question .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"She could have mentioned ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"but didn ' t ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that the FBI ' s renewed background check","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"she pushed for","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"turned up no corroborating information .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Opponents of Judge Kavanaugh say","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"that Republicans are brushing by Ford ' s allegation .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"As Collins demonstrated ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"that ' s not true .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"It ' s simply that there isn ' t enough evidence","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to credit her charge ;","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"in fact the evidence cuts the other way , even under the \" more likely than not \" standard","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"that Collins set out .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"She spoke , with conviction , of how important she believes","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"the Me Too movement is .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"But that doesn ' t mean that every accusation must be believed ,","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"or the mere existence of an accusation should be enough","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"to destroy someone ' s reputation and career .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"Collins spent the first part of her remarks","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"defending Kavanaugh ' s jurisprudence , in a bizarre flashback to what the Kavanaugh confirmation was largely","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"- although not entirely -","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"about a few weeks ago .","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"She emphasized how much weight he puts on precedent .","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"This is important to Collins","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"because she hopes","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"the Court will preserve Roe v. Wade .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"We think","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"she ' s wrong to infer from Kavanaugh ' s respect for precedent that Roe has a safe future ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"and , of course , disagree with her on the merits of that execrable decision .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"But we will leave that for another day .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"For now we will only say ,","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"Well done , Senator .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"You have done your institution and yourself proud .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":133,"left":70,"right":132,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":69,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":117,"right":131,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":117,"left":112,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":104,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":76,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":72,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":4,"right":71,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":71,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":7,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"l